This tool run was tested on g++ (Ubuntu 4.8.4-2ubuntu1~14.04.4) 4.8.4

Type make to build
Type ./server to run tool
Type make clean to clean

This tool run on localhost (0.0.0.0 or 127.0.0.1) port 8888
Use telnet to connect and send expression

Testcase: 

1+2 -> 3
4*(2+10) -> 48
(12/5) -> 2
(1)) -> INVALID
) 4 + 2 -> INVALID
123*-4 -> INVALID
1*2*3*4*5-6 -> 114
1/(1-2) -> -1
1/0 ->0
( 3 + 2 * 4 ) * 7 -> 77
